{"tid":2295993,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"返屋企驚見女朋友個男同事只著孖煙通","createTime":"2020-11-22T06:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T07:41:08.000Z","uid":60658,"like":9,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e678d9bf6a895921d34601f85cbddaa0d13b8fe","tid":2295993,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"話說我係同我女朋友出面租屋住<br />\n有晚我OT但係漏咗啲嘢喺屋企 咁我又唔算遠咪返去拎<br />\n點知我一開門就見到有個男人坐咗喺梳化 有著衫但係下身得條孖煙通<br />\n之後我問你係邊個 我女朋友就衝忙忙咁走過嚟同我講: 吖 佢係我同事啊~<br />\n佢話因為佢岩岩食唔小心倒瀉嘢落佢度 碌親佢 所以叫佢上去順便俾D藥佢搽<br />\n洗洗條褲.. <br />\n<br />\n雖然我眼見個男仔真係有紅左一撻 而且佢地都有著衫 冇扑過嘢既痕跡<br />\n但我硬係覺得佢地有揸過波之類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我最後選擇左信佢地<br />\n仲請個男仔飲左罐啤酒"},{"pid":"6835bc34379b6178b51ca5ad77e8e97fac411ac0","tid":2295993,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3504d8d83eeed2b1ba1d8f33e2a530a7c9f8dd0a","tid":2295993,"uid":343520,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"舊po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a0aca209fcd02b58649c432a63129a6f739517","tid":2295993,"uid":60658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6835bc34379b6178b51ca5ad77e8e97fac411ac0","tid":2295993,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:44:59.000Z","msg":"笑乜呢？"},{"pid":"96298201df627edc26ee3174f79ba2a6aa75ce3a","tid":2295993,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3504d8d83eeed2b1ba1d8f33e2a530a7c9f8dd0a","tid":2295993,"uid":343520,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"舊po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas